---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Refund Policy · Nevermind">
  <nav class="nav">
    <a href="/">Home</a>
    <a href="/docs">Docs</a>
    <a href="/terms">Terms</a>
    <a href="/refund" aria-current="page">Refunds</a>
  </nav>

  <h1>Refund Policy</h1>
  <p class="muted"><em><!-- HUMAN-REVIEW: Legal copy below is a draft placeholder and must be reviewed by a human before launch. --></em></p>

  <div class="section card">
    <p><em>Last updated: July 2026</em></p>

    <h2>Subscription Cancellation</h2>
    <p>You may cancel your subscription at any time from your <a href="/profile">profile</a> page. Cancellation takes effect at the end of the current billing period. You retain access to paid features until the period ends.</p>

    <h2>Refunds</h2>
    <p>Paid credits are non-refundable except as required by applicable law. If you believe there has been an error in billing, contact us within 30 days and we will review your case.</p>

    <h2>Account Deletion</h2>
    <p>When you delete your account, any active subscription is canceled and your personal data is removed. See our <a href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a> for details.</p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>For billing questions, open an issue at <a href="https://github.com/pablopunk/nvm">github.com/pablopunk/nvm</a>.</p>
  </div>
</Layout>
